<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Payment Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #2ecc71; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .payment-details { background: white; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .amount { font-size: 24px; color: #2ecc71; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸ’³ Payment Confirmed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{clientName}},</p>

            <p>Thank you! Your payment has been successfully processed.</p>

            <div class="payment-details">
                <h3>Payment Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <span class="amount">{{currency}} ${{amount}}</span></p>
                <p><strong>Payment Type:</strong> {{paymentType}}</p>
                <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>You can download your invoice using the link below:</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{invoiceUrl}}" class="button">Download Invoice</a>
            </div>

            <p>Your visa application process will now continue. You'll receive updates as we progress through each stage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2025 Migrantifly Immigration Services</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>